    <briefdescription>
<para>I2C Extended HAL module driver. This file provides firmware functions to manage the following functionalities of I2C Extended peripheral: </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="author"><para>MCD Application Team<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Filter Mode Functions</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>WakeUp Mode Functions</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>FastModePlus Functions</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
